    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874980/extras/212c5ecc4817c167bd694519bb165906.poster.avif?t=1763394703\" width=624 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874980/extras/212c5ecc4817c167bd694519bb165906.webm?t=1763394703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874980/extras/212c5ecc4817c167bd694519bb165906.mp4?t=1763394703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>The game is set in American prisons torn by constant prisoner riots. The player controls a police assault group member and recapturing the prison is his objective.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The gameplay revolves around forming a group of 1-4 players helping each other in cooperative missions against computer-controlled prisoners (playing single is available) and then using firearms and different accessories in order to rescue hostages, reclaim prison and/or fulfill any other main/side objectives.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874980/extras/45f18ff966a50d1a3d622bed0e7d910f.poster.avif?t=1763394703\" width=624 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874980/extras/45f18ff966a50d1a3d622bed0e7d910f.webm?t=1763394703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874980/extras/45f18ff966a50d1a3d622bed0e7d910f.mp4?t=1763394703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> Experience real, true hardcore riot american prison style. No limits! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874980/extras/4348bad73b13dee1e29e5ace12efb760.poster.avif?t=1763394703\" width=624 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874980/extras/4348bad73b13dee1e29e5ace12efb760.webm?t=1763394703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874980/extras/4348bad73b13dee1e29e5ace12efb760.mp4?t=1763394703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">As a member of special police task force, your job is to control and recapture most dangerous computer- controled prisoners. You can do it single handedly with help of computer generated squad or with your friends in full co-op mode </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874980/extras/5f1e5193b62d570b52904e5ac46643c4.poster.avif?t=1763394703\" width=624 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874980/extras/5f1e5193b62d570b52904e5ac46643c4.webm?t=1763394703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874980/extras/5f1e5193b62d570b52904e5ac46643c4.mp4?t=1763394703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Immerse in a world full of dangerous convictas and rioters ready to take what they want without remorse!</p>",
